This is an attempt to write an Internet-Draft level
document, setting out the Test Anything Protocol (TAP)
as a language for storing, recording and summarizing
automated testing results.

For more details, please see:
 - http://www.testanything.org/ (TAP website)
 - http://testanything.org/wiki/index.php/TAP_at_IETF:_Draft_Standard
 - https://www.ietf.org/mailman/listinfo/tap (mailing list)
